weighted sums of (central) chi squared random variables:
\deqn{\sum_{k = 1}^\infty v_k^2 \chi^2_{d_{p, k}},}
where
\deqn{d_{p, k} := {{p + k - 3}\choose{p - 2}} + {{p + k - 2}\choose{p - 2}}}
